{"tid":677229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫師開刀邊大跳嘻哈 病患被搞到終身癱瘓","createTime":"2018-05-25T04:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T04:40:10.000Z","uid":73531,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e12d252a1a6c51108c8ec6570c95f5072f888805","tid":677229,"uid":73531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/121810_995514402f3c50eabdf57ec8d62599b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F121810_995514402f3c50eabdf57ec8d62599b7.png&h=5baf5536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美國喬治亞州一名整形外科醫生鮑媞（Windell Davis Boutte），日前在幫病人進行手術時，竟然直接在手術房內上演「醫院有嘻哈」。（圖／翻攝自太陽報 , 2018.5.24）<br />\n<br />\n綜合外國媒體報導，鮑媞日前在幫病患進行手術時，竟然一邊聽嘻哈音樂，還一邊手舞足蹈，看起來十分陶醉，完全不顧病人死活。同事事後將拍下的影片放上網路和網友分享，結果引來爭議。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，當時可奈露絲雖然被轉送至另一間醫院急救，但缺氧已經造成她腦部出現嚴重損傷，如今她已全身癱瘓，一輩子都得這樣活下去。利伯難過地表示，母親只是想在參加婚禮之前變得更漂亮，才去整形，不料卻換得一輩子當「活死人」的下場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://life.tw/?app=view&amp;no=790083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flife.tw%2F%3Fapp%3Dview%26no%3D790083&d=sETKHKOC8XK5OnScn6%2Bzn5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=a71699cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://life.tw/?app=view&amp;no=790083</a>"},{"pid":"7a5901698ab64225b1f44cca4cd0251985167c1a","tid":677229,"uid":34410,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"力架學咩人做醫生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  返去做歌手算啦"},{"pid":"dc5fff3ce6c87f767f3eb91517c95ea50d03c5e2","tid":677229,"uid":154176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:37:21.000Z","msg":"舞動奇蹟"},{"pid":"4b228fc25a4b5de5811fe9dd4509a5d3a1620463","tid":677229,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a5901698ab64225b1f44cca4cd0251985167c1a","tid":677229,"uid":34410,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"力架學咩人做醫生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces